{"tid":505061,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解係一個極靜安既環境入面隻耳就會有d轟轟聲","createTime":"2017-12-20T17:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T18:03:00.000Z","uid":3558,"like":108,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"04fd5af580a39ce704de7d4103a253698677ae0c","tid":505061,"uid":3558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:20:02.000Z","msg":"即係訓教果陣間房係好寧靜 之後隻耳就會有一段好穩定既轟轟聲係耳入面 如果開個風扇整小小聲出黎 咁d軒轟聲又會無左 其實果d轟轟聲係咪正係會出現係好靜既時候先會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔識形容所以用住轟轟聲頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0badbb2c15a9248358828b02729bfcee33d857ca","tid":505061,"uid":100760,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:23:56.000Z","msg":"明你講咩，唔知點解"},{"pid":"c45b4a3ea2b613295c4dd131e7bb843722492271","tid":505061,"uid":3558,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:31:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明你講咩，唔知點解</blockquote><br />\n越靜越嘈 搞到訓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b324c507960e22f0496bcd939ddd5dafdc061dc","tid":505061,"uid":3558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:40:51.000Z","msg":"原來個topic打錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4199d187b20fc54f4e9f9ae60eafed07c842e97","tid":505061,"uid":61510,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:42:27.000Z","msg":"我知你的意思，但我覺得好舒服"},{"pid":"103be5691bca997ef423c277ff523b6c6bdf8774","tid":505061,"uid":3558,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T17:46:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我知你的意思，但我覺得好舒服</blockquote><br />\n竟然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通我有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" cl